1
00:00:09,575 --> 00:00:10,407
Counting down

2
00:00:11,053 --> 00:00:13,869
Three, two, one

3
00:00:14,192 --> 00:00:15,438
Are you ready?

4
00:00:18,625 --> 00:00:19,346
Ready!

5
00:01:01,859 --> 00:01:05,123
In the past, when people sought knowledge

6
00:01:06,100 --> 00:01:08,203
They turned to the Tree of Wisdom

7
00:01:14,729 --> 00:01:18,625
Today, we use it to save Sumeru

8
00:01:19,275 --> 00:01:20,555
And the whole world

9
00:01:23,065 --> 00:01:25,380
These boughs that nurtured learning

10
00:01:26,533 --> 00:01:29,621
Must not become tools for destroying the world

11
00:01:49,852 --> 00:01:50,669
Stop...

12
00:01:51,950 --> 00:01:55,277
Please, stop... End this transformation...

13
00:02:15,235 --> 00:02:18,899
You would shut down Irminsul just to stop me?

14
00:02:19,645 --> 00:02:20,870
You fools

15
00:02:21,457 --> 00:02:25,227
I have all the time in the world...

